import React from "react";
import { Container, InputGroup, Form } from "react-bootstrap";
function ToDoList() {
  return (
      <Container>
          

          
      <InputGroup className="mb-3">
        <Form.Control
          placeholder="Name"
          aria-describedby="inputGroup-sizing-default"
        />
      </InputGroup>

      <InputGroup className="mb-3">
        <Form.Control
          placeholder="Title"
          aria-describedby="inputGroup-sizing-default"
        />
      </InputGroup>

      <InputGroup className="mb-3">
        <Form.Control
          placeholder="Description"
          aria-describedby="inputGroup-sizing-default"
        />
      </InputGroup>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default ToDoList;
